text: Harsdorf is a municipality in Kulmbach in Bavaria in Germany. ==City arrangement== Harsdorf is arranged in the following boroughs: * Altenreuth * Brauneck * Harsdorf * Haselbach * Hettersreuth * Holzlucken * Lettenhof * Oberlaitsch /Seyerhaus * Oberlohe * Ritterleithen * Sandreuth * Unitz * Unterlohe * Zettmeisel ==References== Category:Kulmbach (district)
title: Harsdorf
